    "description": "This function is a decorator that is used to add generated special methods to classes, as described below. The @dataclass decorator examines the class to find fields. A field is defined as a class variable that has a type annotation. With two exceptions described below, nothing in @dataclass examines the type specified in the variable annotation. The order of the fields in all of the generated methods is the order in which they appear in the class definition. The @dataclass decorator will add...",
